01:01:42,200 --> 01:01:44,100
To je vaše rádio?

870
01:01:45,000 --> 01:01:46,000
Jaký hluk?

871
01:01:47,622 --> 01:01:48,640
Nic.

872
01:01:54,800 --> 01:01:55,500
Hele.

873
01:01:56,313 --> 01:01:58,090
Nedotýkej se jen tak mého auta.

874
01:02:13,100 --> 01:02:14,000
Ohh.

